title: Hour 2 – The Cowboys Now Face Pressure To Re-sign Dak Prescott. Guest – Stephen Holder
itunes:title: Hour 2 – The Cowboys Now Face Pressure To Re-sign Dak Prescott. Guest – Stephen Holder
description:
Jason Smith and Doug Gottlieb sit in for Dan Patrick and explain how the Carson Wentz trade impacts contract negotiations between the Cowboys and Dak Prescott. Colts insider Stephen Holder stops by to explain why Carson Wentz can work in Indianapolis.Plus, is Deshaun Watson willing to sit out next season until he gets what he wants?
